metadata.name: Goddess of peace
metadata.description:
When Pandora opened the box that Zeus has given her, the Goddess of peace fell asleep.
Humanity has witnessed many wars which has been started with tribal wars continued by world wars.
Human kills and been killed just for their own selfishness and power.
Today at 2022 the Goddess is waken and with her own unique strategy she is working hard to return peace and tranquility to the world and show that human's benefit is peace for all.
